msgstr "MISSION : FINIR LE DIDACTICIEL"

#. This is the text body of a logbook page.
#: po/tutorial.py:354
msgid ""
"Try to house a total of 50 or more inhabitants in your city by providing more "
"residential buildings."
msgstr ""
"Essayez de loger au moins 50 habitants dans votre ville en fournissant plus "
"de résidences."

#. This is the text body of a logbook page.
#: po/tutorial.py:356
msgid ""
"Once you are able to keep an economy running which can satisfy this amount of "
"consumers, you are ready to discover new Unknown Horizons!"
msgstr ""
"Dès que votre économie pourra satisfaire ce nombre de consommateurs vous "
"serez prêt à découvrir d'autres - Horizons Inconnus !"

#. This is the text body of a logbook page.
#: po/tutorial.py:358
msgid ""
"You also need enough money to keep this economy running, so a positive "
"balance (check in the warehouse tab 'Account') is required."
msgstr ""
"Vous avez aussi besoin de suffisamment d'argent pour maintenir l'économie, "
